      • collectCalls

        public static EList<CallSequenceItem> collectCalls(Process process,
                                                   EMap<ModeLabel,ModeLiteral> modes,
                                                   Function<CallSequenceItem,Boolean> filter)
        Traverse the call graph of a process and collect all items of the call sequences. Collection can be restricted to specific modes and filtered by a lambda expression.
        Parameters:
        process - process (Task or ISR)
        modes - list of mode literals that should be considered
        filter - lambda expression (e.g. "a -> a instanceof TaskRunnableCall")
        Returns:
        List of CallSequenceItems

        Traverse the call graph of a process and collect all items of the call sequences. Collection can be restricted to specific modes and filtered by class.
